videos.headline: Olson walks onto field during senior night
videos.description: USC long snapper Jake Olson is escorted onto the field during senior night before the Trojans' game vs. Notre Dame.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Olson walks onto field during senior night) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Malepeai finds the end zone for early score
videos.description: USC RB Vavae Malepeai takes the handoff, finds the hole and runs into the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Finke just gets across goal line for TD
videos.description: Notre Dame QB Ian Book lobs a pass to WR Chris Finke who makes a great catch and just gets across for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Pittman leaps high to make a great catch
videos.description: USC QB JT Daniels sends a pass 35 yards downfield to WR Michael Pittman Jr. who jumps high to make a spectacular catch.

videos.headline: USC holds 10-7 lead at halftime
videos.description: Vavae Malepeai puts USC up early against Notre Dame. After the Trojans add a field goal, the Fighting Irish respond on Chris Finke's TD catch.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (USC holds 10-7 lead at halftime) 2018/11/24 ESHEET SotFull

videos.headline: Williams breaks loose for 52-yard score
videos.description: Notre Dame RB Dexter Williams finds the hole and speeds past the defense for a 52-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Jones' TD catch-and-run extends Notre Dame's lead late
videos.description: Notre Dame QB Ian Book tosses a pass to RB Tony Jones Jr. who makes a cut and gets a nice block as he walks into the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Notre Dame holds off USC
videos.description: Ian Book throws for 352 yards, two touchdowns and an interception as the Fighting Irish beat USC 24-17.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Notre Dame holds off USC) 2018/11/24 ESHEET SOTFull
